1173
00:53:41,711 --> 00:53:44,046
OPEN

1174
00:53:45,114 --> 00:53:46,849
HOW DID IT TURN OUT?

1175
00:53:47,850 --> 00:53:49,051
Man, it's excellent.

1176
00:53:50,886 --> 00:53:53,456
THE BUN HARVEST FINALLY BEGINS

1177
00:53:55,091 --> 00:53:56,659
POKE

1178
